These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, iris, lily, bellflower
House: farmhouse, victorian, colonial, futuristic
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, brazilian, malaysian, british
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, biathlon, surfing
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, mauve, orange, blood-red
 1. the spanish is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 2. the victorian house is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 3. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the person who growslily is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 9. the malaysian is the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the person who likes orange is the brazilian##1
11. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Flower          | iris    | lily      | dahlia  | bellflower     |
| House         | futuristic    | colonial   | farmhouse | victorian      |
| Nationality   | brazilian       | spanish | malaysian     | british    |
| Sport   | surfing | parkour         | baseball  | biathlon    |
| Color           | orange      | blood-red       | grey | mauve |

