.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, paramedic, manager, electrician
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, red, amber, light-blue
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, pall-mall, old-henry, chaman
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike, car, ship
City: paris, boston, rome, liverpool
 1. the person who likes red is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the electrician is on the far right##1
 5. the chef is on the right of the paramedic##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the manager##1
 7. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 8. the person driving the bike is the chaman-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes amber is the old-henry-smoker##1
10. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the manager is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Job      | paramedic      | chef     | manager    | electrician |
| Color   | orange | red   | amber   | light-blue           |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | chaman     | old-henry    | tiparillo         |
| Transport           | ship         | bike | car     | snowmobile        |
| City         | paris     | liverpool  | boston | rome       |

