.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, disco, d&b, ambient
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, reading, chess, drawing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, mirinda, almond-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, brown, ivory, black
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, fantasy, scientific, western
 1. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
 2. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 3. the fan of d&b is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the fan of disco is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the person watching western movies is the fan of d&b##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Music-Genre          | techno    | ambient      | d&b  | disco   |
| Hobby   | drawing     | chess      | reading | puzzles      |
| Beverage           | soy-milk       | 7up         | almond-milk  | mirinda         |
| Color         | grey | brown | ivory  | black |
| Movie-Genre     | scientific       | horror         | western   | fantasy        |

