.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, blend, bolivar, swisher
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, manager, designer, musician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, classical, funk, country
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, climbing, volleyball, rugby
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia, bellflower, zinnia
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the musician is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 7. the fan of country is on the far right##1
 8. the musician is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the left of the project-manager##1
10. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
12. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar      | bolivar   | swisher   | blend      | chaman     |
| Job          | designer     | project-manager   | musician | manager |
| Music-Genre   | classical | funk | d&b   | country       |
| Sport           | climbing       | surfing      | rugby     | volleyball |
| Flower     | balloon-flower    | bellflower     | zinnia     | begonia     |

