House: farmhouse, victorian, tower, ranch-style
City: hannover, boston, colone, edinburgh
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, r&b, jazz, punk
 1. the farmhouse house is the fan of punk##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
 3. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
 4. the fan of r&b is the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the tower house is on the far right##1
 7. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 8. the fan of punk is the farmhouse house##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is the fan of jazz##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of punk##1
11. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the fan of punk##1
12. the victorian house is on the far left##1
13. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
14. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
