.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, bartender, teacher, mechanic
City: edinburgh, miami, rome, san-francisco
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, zucchini, apricot, asparagus
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, lily, daisy, rose
 1. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the mechanic is the person eating asparagus##1
 4. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the bartender##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
10. the person eating apricot is the person who growsrose##1
11. the teacher is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
12. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Job         | bartender   | teacher | mechanic    | project-manager  |
| City   | san-francisco    | edinburgh | rome      | miami |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | cola | hot-chocolate         | milk  |
| Food         | cranberry  | apricot     | asparagus | zucchini     |
| Flower     | sunflower      | rose       | daisy         | lily         |

