 7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
10. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
