.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, march, june
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, rat, horse
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, tulip, balloon-flower
House: art-deco, victorian, palace, townhouse
There 4 different types of food: lemon, corn, grapes, apple
 1. the person who growslily is on the right of the palace house##1
 2. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
 3. the person eating lemon is the palace house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growslily is the victorian house##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating apple##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating corn##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the art-deco house is the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
12. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
13. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |      3       |       4       |
| Birthday    | february        | january       | june         | march |
| Pet       | goat       | goldfish | horse      | rat     |
| Flower         | tulip | zinnia      | balloon-flower | lily       |
| House       | art-deco      | townhouse     | palace     | victorian    |
| Food   | grapes        | corn    | lemon     | apple         |

