 3. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
 4. the project-manager is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is the mechanic##1
 6. the firefighter is on the far right##1
 7. the ranch-style house is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the wooden house##1
11. the person driving the boat is the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the wooden house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Birthday      | june     | may      | november    | july           |
