.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
4 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, scrabble, go
House: tower, craftsman, cape-cod, colonial
City: berlin, marseilles, london, colone
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, american, polish, russian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, game, aristoff, tiparillo
 1. the polish is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 2. the tower house is the person traveling to berlin##1
 3. the turkish is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the american##1
 8. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person playing billiard is the game-smoker##1
10. the person playing go is the american##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the craftsman house##1
12. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Game    | billiard     | mah-jongg  | go       | scrabble      |
| House       | cape-cod    | colonial        | tower  | craftsman      |
| City         | marseilles  | colone | berlin | london |
| Nationality         | turkish | russian          | american         | polish      |
| Cigar   | game     | baccarat     | aristoff       | tiparillo          |

