.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, white, purple, ivory
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, pop, house, blues
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, musician, chef, police-officer
House: colonial, wooden, craftsman, cottage
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, aconite, poppy, marigold
 1. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
 2. the person who likes white is the police-officer##1
 3. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left of the colonial house##1
 5. the fan of house is the person who likes purple##1
 6. the fan of blues is the person who likes ivory##1
 7. the fan of pop is on the right of the musician##1
 8. the colonial house is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 9. the person who growsaconite is the chef##1
10. the chef is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes white##1
12. the fan of blues is on the left of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Color      | ivory       | purple      | white      | chestnut    |
| Music-Genre         | blues | house | pop | indie  |
| Job   | chef    | musician     | police-officer      | analyst |
