The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, daffodil, zinnia, poppy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, soy-milk, tea
 1. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 4. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person who likes black is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person who growspoppy is the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1
13. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

